## Thermal Tuning

| Parameter | Effect | Typical range |
|-----------|--------|--------------|
| `R_core_K_W` | Core cooling resistance | 0.5–5 K/W |
| `R_surface_K_W` | Surface-to-ambient | 1–10 K/W |
| `C_core_J_K` | Thermal inertia | 30–100 J/K |
| `dUdT_positive` | Entropic heat magnitude | –0.0001 to –0.001 V/K |

### Temperature too high?
1. Reduce C-rate in CC stages
2. Add pre-cooling pause
3. Lower `R_surface_K_W` (better cooling, e.g. active thermal management)

