## Degradation Model Tuning

Calibrate `fade_prefactor` and `activation_energy_J_mol` using aging dataset:

```matlab
% Fit to n_cycle vs Q_retention data from Battery Archive
loss_data = [50, 0.02; 100, 0.035; 200, 0.065; 500, 0.12];  % [cycle, Q_loss_frac]
n = loss_data(:,1);
Q = loss_data(:,2);

% Model: Q_loss = A * n^0.5 (at fixed T)
A_fit = Q ./ sqrt(n);
fade_prefactor = mean(A_fit);
fprintf('Fitted prefactor: %.3e\n', fade_prefactor);
```

