## Common Issues & Fixes

| Symptom | Likely cause | Fix |
|---------|-------------|-----|
| `ode15s` fails / too slow | Stiff system, small timesteps | Increase AbsTol, use `spmJacobian` |
| Voltage exceeds V_max | Current too high | Reduce I_max, add voltage event |
| `fmincon` diverges | Poor initial guess | Warm-start from multi-stage profile |
| theta_neg > 1 | Timestep too large | Reduce dt or add capping event |
| SOC oscillates | OCV curve non-monotone at boundaries | Clamp theta to [0.01, 0.99] |
